metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The number of client requests served by the HTTP/S proxy
metricSpecifications.name: RequestCount

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The number of bytes sent as responses from HTTP/S proxy to clients
metricSpecifications.name: ResponseSize

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The time calculated from when the client request was received by the HTTP/S proxy until the client acknowledged the last response byte from the HTTP/S proxy
metricSpecifications.name: TotalLatency

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: This is the ratio of the total bytes served from the cache compared to the total response bytes
metricSpecifications.name: ByteHitRatio

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The percentage of all the client requests for which the response status code is 4XX
metricSpecifications.name: Percentage4XX

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The percentage of all the client requests for which the response status code is 5XX
metricSpecifications.name: Percentage5XX

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The number of bytes sent as requests from clients to AFDX.
metricSpecifications.name: RequestSize

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The time calculated from when the request was sent by AFDX edge to the backend until AFDX received the last response byte from the backend.
metricSpecifications.name: OriginLatency

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The number of requests sent from AFDX to origin.
metricSpecifications.name: OriginRequestCount

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The percentage of successful health probes from AFDX to backends.
metricSpecifications.name: OriginHealthPercentage

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The number of client requests processed by the Web Application Firewall
metricSpecifications.name: WebApplicationFirewallRequestCount

metricSpecifications.displayDescription: The number of JS challenge requests evaluated by the Web Application Firewall
metricSpecifications.displayName: Web Application Firewall JS Challenge Request Count
metricSpecifications.name: WebApplicationFirewallJsRequestCount
